## Pear Shaped Sapphire and Diamond Engagement Ring

[![Pear diamond engagement ring in rose gold — warm pink-copper metal with white pear diamond solitaire on Blue Nile](/images/pear-diamond-engagement-ring-rose-gold.avif)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings?MetalType=all&Diamonds=Dia&ShapeID=Pear&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)
*Rose gold pear diamond engagement ring — the warm pink metal flatters H–J color diamonds and pairs beautifully with colored stone accents. **[Shop rose gold pear rings on Blue Nile →](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings?MetalType=all&Diamonds=Dia&ShapeID=Pear&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)***

The sapphire-and-pear-diamond combination is one of the most requested colored-stone engagement ring configurations. There are two distinct versions buyers ask about, and they are completely different rings:

**Version 1: Pear sapphire center with diamond accents.** The center stone is a pear-cut natural blue sapphire. Diamond side stones or a diamond halo frame the sapphire. The Blue Nile Classic Pear Shaped Sapphire Engagement Ring in platinum at **[$2,610](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/classic-pear-shaped-sapphire-engagement-ring-in-platinum-item-194499?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** is an example — pear sapphire in a clean platinum prong setting. The Kate Middleton effect is real: pear sapphire engagement rings have been persistently popular since 2010.

**Version 2: Pear diamond center with sapphire side stones.** The center stone is a pear-cut diamond. Sapphire baguettes, round sapphires, or oval sapphires flank the center diamond. This configuration is less common in off-the-shelf catalogs and typically requires a custom setting. The visual effect is striking — the blue of the sapphires against a white pear diamond reads elegantly and distinctly.

For pear sapphire engagement rings: natural Ceylon (Sri Lanka) and Madagascar sapphires are the top-tier sourcing countries. The Sapphire and Diamond Double Halo Ring in 14k rose gold at **[$3,535](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/sapphire-and-diamond-double-halo-engagement-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-1-2-ct-tw-item-203378?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** offers a double-halo sapphire setting with diamond accents — a high-impact alternative to the all-diamond pear ring.

